==English==

===Etymology===
Anthony (Tony) Blair, Leader of the British [[Labour Party]], and UK [[prime minister]] at the turn of the twentyfirst century.

===Noun===
'''Blairite'''
# A supporter of Tony Blair, or his [[economic]] or [[political]] [[policies]]

===Adjective===
'''Blairite'''
# Of, or relating to the [[populist]] or [[right wing]] policies introduced by the UK government from 1997-, which were largely seen to a move away from traditional [[Labour]] values.

